 Legion.

>put id in left pocket
 Done.

>examine uniform
 (your uniform)
 Your uniform comprises a white tunic and matching white trousers.  On
 the left breast of the tunic is emblazoned a purple eagle, and though
 you can't see them without the aid of a mirror, you know that there's
 a purple patch on each collar, bearing your insignia of rank.  Below
 your belt the tunic has a pair of pockets.  Your left pocket contains
